metadata.name: SKULLS AND ROSES
metadata.description:
A visual representation of the feelings associated with the NFT space. Roses depict happiness, butterflies symbolise the evolving process, there is no hurry says the hourglass, don't keep monetary goals because it drains the life out of you. Somedays you may find keys to treasure while the other days maybe lonely and empty. A piece full of vibrant shades and neon light effects created using a digital pencil and is completely hand drawn. 

Every bid accounts to a special airdrop, so happy bidding <3
